{"tid":95884,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(港豬)雙糧","createTime":"2017-01-26T11:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T13:02:17.000Z","uid":55347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d65e9cb2649f5609a94aa5ad34eb22131ddcf1a","tid":95884,"uid":55347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:14:40.000Z","msg":"屌 又話公司今年賺左好多錢 會出雙糧又加人工<br />\n<br />\n而家呢？聽日都放假啦 今日都未出 <br />\n<br />\n上年又係咁 問左話會出 之後拖撚到年中先出 中途問都問到口嗅 搞到好似乞衣咁 <br />\n<br />\n我都係想拎返自己應得個分姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n平時老闆係公司成日打飛機自high 話到自己 幾咁有錢 <br />\n<br />\n但一問你出雙糧既事就走左去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話要問吓其他股東 <br />\n<br />\n問咩姐！其他幾個股東都睇你頭 全公司都知架啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無咩事 我出返去做野先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda21846f8994b218a01e9ed5ab3a433986745ca","tid":95884,"uid":55347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:21:43.000Z","msg":"係咪個果以經拎住分雙糧花紅出街威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d551ef0ff291360157a202c86ec3b6230dee06e0","tid":95884,"uid":17896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:23:14.000Z","msg":"樓主，我見你個post ,真係身同感受<br />\n<br />\n有無打算報警？"},{"pid":"4554c921a3b2ac9ec8424c06f94b1425290d063f","tid":95884,"uid":55347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主，我見你個post ,真係身同感受<br />\n<br />\n有無打算報警？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報警有用咩？<br />\n<br />\n我係咪真心左"},{"pid":"a9fae8bec626cd70284e6790540bdfae77ba5888","tid":95884,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:33:17